{"tid":1652052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後絕不拆RB，邊個拆邊個就係鬼","createTime":"2019-10-13T14:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T06:09:32.000Z","uid":161701,"like":59,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"277c00fb9d2c1c016589440e6b1d6f268dfb86da","tid":1652052,"uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"Set完RB之後，<br />\n唔該唔該唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n救護車，消防車，乜撚柒車都唔好放佢入來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家係示緊威呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲做埋d左膠野<br />\n次次睇TVB<br />\n叫開路讓車就最撚大聲，<br />\n但呢聲大大<br />\n但大部份人個腦又停喺度<br />\n各位手足我地係打仗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗都唔諗救護車/消防車後既私家車有冇/係咪卧底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔係卧底<br />\n只要畜龍配合救護車/消防車駛入既時嘅進一步行動<br />\n咁就仆街啦...<br />\n夠啦夠啦夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠鐘帶個腦出來示威啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗清楚點解要set RB，唔好盲目做大愛撚<br />\n你可能大愛一時，但前線斑手足要坐十年監呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2369814a303ebf244b2624b1338ee46d16375cdb","tid":1652052,"uid":26015,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"呢個真.... 手足比人拉就十年...<br />\n開RB既人願意承受呢個風險放狗入黎?.."},{"pid":"a64f7a89ec4c7d2c777dfc88ec0ba2ae51d13198","tid":1652052,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"d80082c01c7f8e98a6f827d7ea82bf8ddf382355","tid":1652052,"uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4beed203d670a78387404f47d167ba1ecd5b028b","tid":1652052,"uid":66049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"唔好再讓俾消防<br />\n今日沙田消防幫狗拆rb"},{"pid":"bfbbc06947cc20e63d9e3c8a6d8d8c1e16d0c0be","tid":1652052,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"唔好再放了<br />\n而家消防救護都被逼幫黑警了"},{"pid":"3655950190d2543cc75f849172e4b562d261d51c","tid":1652052,"uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfbbc06947cc20e63d9e3c8a6d8d8c1e16d0c0be","tid":1652052,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"唔好再放了<br />\n而家消防救護都被逼幫黑警了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:31:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2932cdb86e14cfad008ab119d9f94a181879284d","tid":1652052,"uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"推呀，屌"},{"pid":"370b908868de4cfe6146402ea40db108c47bad57","tid":1652052,"uid":195998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"277c00fb9d2c1c016589440e6b1d6f268dfb86da","tid":1652052,"uid":161701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"Set完RB之後，<br />\n唔該唔該唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n救護車，消防車，乜撚柒車都唔好放佢入來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家係示緊威呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/